|1 |├─TABLE FULL SCAN      |ref_1|1       |3           |
|2 |└─SUBPLAN FILTER       |     |1       |21          |
|3 |  ├─TABLE FULL SCAN    |ref_0|1       |18          |
|4 |  └─TABLE FULL SCAN    |ref_2|1       |3           |
========================================================
